data.name: 0000 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You could hear the sound of a piano coming from an empty music room?

data.name: 0001 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's certainly clichéd, but it's perfectly suitable as one of the new seven wonders.

data.name: 0002 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hey, Haruhi, can't we just leave it at that and go home?

data.name: 0003 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It's bound to be another misunderstanding from the Computer Society.

data.name: 0004 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We absolutely cannot! We've still got three left!

data.name: 0005 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We can't stop until we've checked them all!

data.name: 0008 (390.ja) TSURUYA (鶴屋)
data.value: Yoo-hoo! How're you doing, Mikuru, Haru-nyan and the rest?

data.name: 0009 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: Tsuruya#W10…#W10…#W20What's going on?

data.name: 0010 (390.ja) TSURUYA (鶴屋)
data.value: Well I was just in the area, you know—

data.name: 0011 (390.ja) TSURUYA (鶴屋)
data.value: I heard Mikuru was at school and stuff—I thought, how 'bout I drop on by?

data.name: 0012 (390.ja) TSURUYA (鶴屋)
data.value: I'm like, jumping in to look after you peeps a bit.

data.name: 0017 (390.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: According to their testimony, the piano could be heard every day at about the same time.

data.name: 0018 (390.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: #DP

data.name: 0019 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hmm#W20…#W10…#W20 Got it!

data.name: 0020 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Got what?

data.name: 0021 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's got to be the ghost of a beautiful prodigy pianist girl who died a tragic death!

data.name: 0022 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Why do you just randomly assume it's a prodigy or a girl?

data.name: 0023 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That's#W20…#W10…

data.name: 0024 (390.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Because that sounds more interesting, obviously!

data.name: 0028 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: It's quite a mysterious melody, isn't it.

data.name: 0029 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: It's like it's trying to warn us of something.

data.name: 0032 (390.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Data lifeforms do not require any form.

data.name: 0033 (390.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: As long as there is something to observe it, its existance probability can increase.

data.name: 0034 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Observe#W20…#W10…#W10?

data.name: 0035 (390.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: The music is for that purpose solely.

data.name: 0036 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hey, what does that mean, Nagato?!

data.name: 0037 (390.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: At the present my role is to gather data.

data.name: 0040 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: Put an end to the training camp#W20…#W10…#W20?

data.name: 0041 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That's right. Since the school is in danger…

data.name: 0042 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …it'd be best to get everyone out as soon as we can.

data.name: 0043 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: That's#W20…#W20…#W30classified information.

data.name: 0045 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: I need permission if I want to drastically interfere with Suzumiya's actions.

data.name: 0046 (390.ja) MIKURU (朝比奈)
data.value: …I'm sorry, Kyon.

data.name: 0049 (390.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It's not looking good—the fact Suzumiya has already come so far.

data.name: 0050 (390.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Damn it. If it's come to this, someone… the piano—
